[[span style="color: #A38800; font-size: 4em; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Poiret One', cursive; word-break: normal;"]]
= Ambrose Newcastle[[/span]]

@@ @@
@@ @@
= [[span style="color: #A38800; font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: bold; font-family: 'Poiret One', cursive; border-bottom: 1px solid #A38800;"]]@@ DO NOT IGNORE @@[[/span]]

Good evening, this is our 1385th reminder to please refer to our original offer regarding the trade of various Avisocc players under your ownership. We believe that all of England should be able to experience the lively and unique taste of these wonderful fowls. Surely you understand the potential ticket sales that would come out of a live exhibition, followed by a meal!

Please...

-Chaz Ambrose

